                LRA Cloud Operations.
              </p>
              <div
                class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 mb-5 pb-5 border-b border-gray-100"
              >
                {
                  [
                    'Cisco Systems',
                    'Windows Server',
                    'Active Directory',
                    'Firewalls',
                    'VoIP',
                    'VPN',
